{"tid":694190,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"星島報紙佬係咪冇野寫？","createTime":"2018-06-08T06:05:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T06:14:15.000Z","uid":139244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7f022f8f71d14c9a1c0de86c6ed36252d48585e0","tid":694190,"uid":139244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T06:05:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/08/140515_0eb71309cc0ed78482e7eeb88f045395.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F08%2F140515_0eb71309cc0ed78482e7eeb88f045395.png&h=5b122215&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】劉鳴煒雖然是劉鑾雄(大劉)兒子，出生於富貴之家，但他其實一啲都唔離地，一直非常關心香港年青人的成長及發展，致力為本港的青少年事務出謀獻策。<br />\n<br />\n　　要了解青年人的想法，最直接的方法當然是親身接觸他們，所以近日劉鳴煒就化身中學生，走進一間中學班房，直接與青年人對話，聆聽他們的心聲，更在社交網上載了幾張著校服的照片。他留言話：「It's part of my job to go undercover into schools to gather information about young people. (潛伏在學校收集年青人資料是我工作的一部分)＃逃學威龍 ＃扮中四學生唔容易 ＃真係有功課要做」雖然劉鳴煒今年已37歲，但穿上校服的他坐在其他學生身邊時，又沒有太大違和感，更有網友講笑咁話他好似食咗防腐劑！"},{"pid":"aa0e44d2756602b0da5a077b4e46168287ea6c0e","tid":694190,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T06:07:11.000Z","msg":"但他其實一啲都唔離地<br />\n<br />\no rly<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45af5624f868b5d2b0601205d6f03f64002c829","tid":694190,"uid":139244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa0e44d2756602b0da5a077b4e46168287ea6c0e","tid":694190,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T06:07:11.000Z","msg":"但他其實一啲都唔離地<br />\n<br />\no rly<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T06:10:26.000Z","msg":"有錢真好，咁就可上報紙，打飛機"},{"pid":"2b49d255751ff9845a1bd59d6c80271c92c4dc37","tid":694190,"uid":135957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T06:14:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}